  <summary date="2019-08-20T22:10:29Z" status="Introduced in House">Protecting Job Opportunities for Borrowers Act or the Protecting JOBs Act

This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to prohibit states from suspending, revoking, or denying driver's licenses, teaching licenses, or professional licenses based solely on individuals' default or delinquency on student loans.</summary>
